Looking for a Toyota Highlander near Washington?

The Toyota Highlander is a mid-sized near-luxury crossover competing in a crowded segment where just about every major auto manufacturer has a hat in the ring. What makes the Highlander successful is its blend of technology, convenience and Toyota durability at the right price. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect Highlander for you.

Autotrader has 2,391 Toyota Highlanders for sale near Washington, DC, including a Certified 2015 Toyota Highlander AWD Limited V6, a Used 2011 Toyota Highlander 4WD, and a Used 2011 Toyota Highlander Limited.

Not sure if a Highlander is the right fit for you?
